Ernie Van Den Heuvel, president and
chief executive officer of Hand Trux, discusses the company's 
outlook and its emphasis on products being "Made in America." 
Van Den Heuvel talked with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  and Vonnie 
Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage" on March 26, 
2012.  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 21:53
 